Wellness Center


Resources & Services


Literature Library & Videos






Literature Library & Videos
A resource center equipped with pamphlets, brochures, and other items covering everything from stress and nutrition to relationships and abstinence. The literature library is self-serve and is a great place to obtain accurate information. This resource is open to the registered UIC students.






